snippet.title: Fireside Prototype | Gameplay Preview
snippet.description:
Wishlist Fireside on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1722700/Fireside/
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/QRhHR6X
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/EmergoE

We're Emergo Entertainment a small indie studio from Bayreuth / Germany working on our first commercial game "Fireside". Join us as we face the highs and lows of professional gamedevlopment. This series is about learning together so don't hesitate to leave any feedback & questions you might have!
